<p>As BNB transitions from BEP-2 to a more robust EVM-compatible framework, the landscape of on-chain governance undergoes constant refinement. The integration with decentralized applications (dApps) and the development of non-fungible token standards add layers to governance models. Moreover, cross-chain functionality amplifies the need for seamless interoperability.</p>



