<li><strong>Participation Guidelines</strong>: Binance encourages the community to actively participate in the proposal process. To ensure fair and transparent voting, guidelines are in place to prevent manipulation or fraudulent activities. These guidelines may include requirements such as holding a minimum amount of BNB or having a specified account age.</li>



